# vite+vue3项目打包ts报错

## JSX element implicitly has type 'any' because no interface 'JSX.IntrinsicElements' exists.

# 现象

![Alternative Text][1723990676763]

报了一堆错

解决方案：

tsconfig.json中添加以下配置

```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "jsx": "preserve",
    "jsxImportSource": "vue"
  }
}
```
